=== Fossil genera ===

The following fossil genera are known:

* &quot;Actiornis&quot; (Late Eocene of England)
* ?&quot;Dakotornis&quot; (Late Paleocene of North Dakota, USA)
* ?&quot;Minggangia&quot; (Late Eocene of China)
* &quot;Rhynchaeites&quot; (Early to Middle Eocene of England and Germany, potentially Denmark and Wyoming, USA)
* ?&quot;Vadaravis&quot; (Early Eocene of Wyoming, USA)

